@*
    Inline status pill for an audit row's Action — Created / Updated /
    Deleted / Denied. Uses the existing enki-status-pill theme so it
    looks the same as Job/Tenant status badges elsewhere on the site.

    Created  → "active"   (live / current)
    Updated  → "inactive" (modified — neutral warning)
    Deleted  → "archived" (muted — removed)
    Denied   → "inactive" (privilege-boundary signal)

    Shared by AuditHistoryTile, MasterAudit, IdentityAudit, and the
    per-tenant audit page so the visual language stays consistent.
*@

<span class="enki-status-pill @PillClass">@Action</span>

